description: A collection of circles in a sideways crescent-shaped formation with three lines of circles extending downwards from the bottom, a short line of circles extending outwards from the left side and two thin almond-shaped formations extending upwards from the top. Each circle has a different number in the center denoting how many lines stem from that point. There is a very dark brown triangle on the left side of the crescent-shaped formation and a thinner dark brown triangle on the right side.
